snippet.title: Hive Jump 2: Survivors | 1.0 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Hive Jump 2: Survivors is now available on Steam and GOG!
Play now: https://bit.ly/3JJPAkz

As the lone survivor of your squad, you're left on an alien planet with just your weapon, a jumping jetpack, and enough courage to keep fighting. Kill off insect swarms and transform their valuable guts into explosive upgrades. Become an agent of vengeance in this survivors-like, bullet-heaven action roguelike! 

STUDIO: @GraphiteLab  
SUBSCRIBE: https://bit.ly/3DZMUMP 
DISCORD: https://bit.ly/3HwLoDF
TWITTER: https://x.com/midwestgamesco
TIKTOK: https://www.tiktok.com/@midwest_games
